I ran this prompt through Claude Sonnet and Opus and ChatGPT 4o and o1 , an=
d here were the results (links have spoilers!):

Time Correct Output Claude Sonnet 14 seconds No link ( https://claude.site/=
artifacts/6e8227b8-cb38-44d3-906b-d4bba12fe0a3 ) Claude Opus 20 seconds No =
N/A ChatGPT 4o 12 seconds No link ( https://chatgpt.com/share/66e8172f-9858=
